        watching more of them over the summer, and was persuaded to make a <a
          href="https://letterboxd.com/yihui"
          target="_blank">Letterboxd</a
        >, so I have that too. I also have <a
          href="https://bsky.app/profile/yihui.bsky.social"
          target="_blank">Bluesky</a
        >. Though, most times, I'm on <a
          href="https://twitter.com/_yihui"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        >.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
